  "Optimization means finding the best possible value (maximum or minimum) of an objective function within a set of constraints. Linear programming is one method of optimization.": "优化是指在一系列制约因素中找到一个目标功能的最佳可能价值(最大或最低),线性方案编制是一种优化方法。",
